description: This file defines APIs and data structures for DNS diagnostics and NSLookup diagnostics in a C-based data model library. It includes function declarations for getting and setting diagnostic parameters, as well as managing diagnostic result entries.

methods.name: NSLookupDiagnostics_GetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Retrieves a boolean parameter value for the NSLookupDiagnostics object.

methods.name: NSLookupDiagnostics_SetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Sets a boolean parameter value for the NSLookupDiagnostics object.

methods.name: NSLookupDiagnostics_GetParamIntValue
methods.description: Retrieves an integer parameter value for the NSLookupDiagnostics object.

methods.name: NSLookupDiagnostics_SetParamIntValue
methods.description: Sets an integer parameter value for the NSLookupDiagnostics object.

methods.name: NSLookupDiagnostics_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves a ULONG parameter value for the NSLookupDiagnostics object.

methods.name: NSLookupDiagnostics_SetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Sets a ULONG parameter value for the NSLookupDiagnostics object.

methods.name: NSLookupDiagnostics_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves a string parameter value for the NSLookupDiagnostics object.

methods.name: NSLookupDiagnostics_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets a string parameter value for the NSLookupDiagnostics object.

methods.name: NSLookupDiagnostics_Rollback
methods.description: Rolls back changes to NSLookupDiagnostics parameters.

methods.name: Result_GetEntryCount
methods.description: Returns the count of diagnostic result entries.

methods.name: Result_GetEntry
methods.description: Retrieves a specific diagnostic result entry by index.

methods.name: Result_IsUpdated
methods.description: Checks if the diagnostic results have been updated.

methods.name: Result_Synchronize
methods.description: Synchronizes the result entries with the current data.

methods.name: Result_GetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Retrieves a boolean value from a result entry.

methods.name: Result_GetParamIntValue
methods.description: Retrieves an integer value from a result entry.

methods.name: Result_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves a ULONG value from a result entry.

methods.name: Result_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves a string value from a result entry.
